name: MembershipDues
description:
The last known state of member's dues in a group.

The state is preserved across a member leaving and re-joining a group,
so that a user may have a dues record in a group while not being a member of that group.

fields.name: graceEndDate
fields.description: The last known dues grace period end date. Empty if a member has never been in dues grace.

fields.name: method
fields.description: The last known membership dues payment method.

fields.name: paidEndDate
fields.description: The last known dues payment period end date. Empty if a member has never paid dues.

fields.name: status
fields.description: The last known membership dues status.

fields.name: trialEndDate
fields.description: The last known dues trial period end date. Empty if a member has never enrolled into a trial.
